  "description": "A single sine strand draped over a trefoil knot. Minimal braid depth lets the fundamental breathe. Slow sine LFO on pitch adds a living pulse. The silk quality comes from the low resonance filter staying wide open. This is Orbweave at its most pure — one strand, one knot, endless presence.",
